Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.00,0:01:42.00,TopCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,ORGANISM LIMITS
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.08,0:01:43.75,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this is a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.83,0:01:47.92,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I never expected Zombieman to be a\Ntest subject from the House of Evolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.58,0:01:52.33,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I have many memories of Sample No. 66.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.71,0:01:54.75,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,You were an excellent specimen\Nand my only success
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.83,0:01:56.71,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,in my immortality experiments.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.83,0:01:59.75,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,But then, you destroyed the lab\Nand disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.08,0:02:02.04,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,That was over ten years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.50,0:02:04.46,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,And now, you've become a hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.75,0:02:07.25,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,You actually managed to change yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.92,0:02:12.00,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're going to kill me?\NThat's fine too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.13,0:02:14.08,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did the House of Evolution\Ndisappear?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.38,0:02:17.29,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,You can rebuild it as many times\Nas you want, as long as you're alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.75,0:02:19.54,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Answer me, Dr. Genus!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.04,0:02:22.29,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,My research was a failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.38,0:02:26.75,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I witnessed a power that\Nfar surpassed artificial evolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.21,0:02:29.46,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,He removed his limiter.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.79,0:02:30.88,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Limiter?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.00,0:02:32.83,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how much\Nan organism strives
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.92,0:02:35.92,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,there are limits to its growth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.96,0:02:40.13,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,An overabundance of strength is\Na burden to its bearer
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.29,0:02:42.04,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,and can cause malfunctions.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.25,0:02:45.42,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Or they may become a monster who\Nhas lost all humanity
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.50,0:02:47.17,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,and rage out of control.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.75,0:02:49.46,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,For that reason
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.54,0:02:52.88,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,God has designed each creature\Nto grow within parameters
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.96,0:02:56.08,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,that allow for survival and\Nthe preservation of reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.96,0:03:34.96,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,And that is what a limiter is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.67,0:03:37.46,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,But he was different.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.58,0:03:40.13,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,By pushing himself\Nbeyond his boundaries
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.21,0:03:43.29,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,he removed his limiter and\Nobtained unfathomable strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.42,0:03:48.42,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Is strength without a limiter\Nsomething one can gain without any cost?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.67,0:03:51.21,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not, he paid a price.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.96,0:03:54.50,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,In exchange for his strength,\Nhe went bald.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.58,0:03:57.63,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,He also suffers from the loneliness\Nthat comes with such overwhelming power.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.71,0:04:01.25,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,After defeating the strongest warrior\Nin my lab’s history with a single punch
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.33,0:04:04.33,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,the look on his face said it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.63,0:04:05.71,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.79,0:04:08.33,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like\Nthe only malfunction caused
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.42,0:04:10.42,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,by your bizarre research\Nwas in your own head.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.92,0:04:15.63,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I have seen many monsters who've\Nignored the limits of their abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.75,0:04:18.83,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Most likely this is far beyond...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.92,0:04:21.25,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,...what you’re imagining.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.54,0:04:23.38,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,The triggers for becoming a monster vary.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.46,0:04:24.71,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,A spiraling obsession or
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.79,0:04:26.96,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,an inferiority complex leading to\Na desire to transform
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.08,0:04:30.04,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,or an explosion of pent-up frustration.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.13,0:04:31.58,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,The causes may vary
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.67,0:04:33.71,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,but in every case their cells\Nsuffer abnormalities
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.79,0:04:35.75,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,and they became mutated creatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.25,0:04:38.17,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Others, like those born\Nfrom my research
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.25,0:04:41.04,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,were deliberately created\Nthrough scientific means.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.33,0:04:44.42,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Many non-human creatures\Nmutate into monstrous forms
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.50,0:04:47.13,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,due to environmental pollution\Nor other factors.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.63,0:04:50.04,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,But that is simply\Nbecoming another species.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.13,0:04:52.25,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,It is not the same as\Nbreaking the limiter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.50,0:04:54.67,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,The Clan of the Seafolk\Nwho attacked City J
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.75,0:04:56.38,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,and the aliens\Nthat appeared in City A
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.46,0:04:58.38,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,can be broadly classified as monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.88,0:05:01.08,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,But they were always creatures\Nlike that from the start
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.17,0:05:04.08,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,and natural enemies of mankind\Nwith an intelligence of their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.46,0:05:09.67,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Heroes possess the great power\Nto confront and fight against them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.79,0:05:12.58,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Those heroes are born with\Nthe potential to become strong
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.71,0:05:15.92,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,and they cultivated it\Nthrough effort and talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.08,0:05:17.92,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Some have undergone\Ncybernetic enhancements
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.00,0:05:21.83,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,or have acquired special abilities\Nthrough human experimentation, like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.00,0:05:24.96,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Some are born as\Nextraordinary geniuses like me
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.04,0:05:26.67,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,or gifted with unique abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.08,0:05:29.38,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,But he was different.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.63,0:05:33.46,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Born ordinary, lived an ordinary life,\Nand possessed no special talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.54,0:05:35.08,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,He was just a regular person.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.17,0:05:37.96,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,But through sheer effort alone\Nhe forced open the door to his limits
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.04,0:05:39.83,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,and shattered his limiter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.29,0:05:42.50,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,The strength of someone\Nwho has removed their limiter
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.58,0:05:45.17,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,and undergone self-evolution\Nis truly remarkable...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.92,0:05:48.42,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Just thinking about it\Nnow makes me laugh
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.50,0:05:51.04,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,at how absurd my own ambitions were.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.58,0:05:54.25,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,One day, you may have\Na chance to meet him too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.58,0:05:57.00,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, he's also a hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.71,0:05:59.33,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any more questions?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.54,0:06:01.63,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,So why takoyaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.04,0:06:04.13,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,While researching human regeneration
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.25,0:06:07.25,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I found a way to endlessly\Nregenerate octopus legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.42,0:06:08.50,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.04,0:06:15.25,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can beat these guys.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.50,0:06:18.33,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They're nothing compared{\i0}\N{\i1}to the old geezer.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.67,0:06:21.21,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe a human\Ncould go this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.46,0:06:25.29,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,It's two against one.\NYou must be pretty strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.75,0:06:30.50,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I was gonna toy\Nwith you a bit, but forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.63,0:06:31.63,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's finish this...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.83,0:06:33.42,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,The real fight starts now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.96,0:06:36.00,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I've figured out all your moves.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.88,0:06:41.50,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll never hit me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.88,0:06:44.96,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,- Old dude...\N- Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.04,0:06:46.38,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,- Oh.\N- Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.83,0:06:53.08,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Old dude... Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.54,0:06:56.21,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Hedro-Jellyfish, what brings you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.50,0:06:59.92,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got a personal grudge\Nwith that guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.25,0:07:01.38,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That bastard...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.42,0:07:04.63,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! That damn brat's got\Nnothing to do with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.79,0:07:18.83,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.00,0:07:20.04,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.29,0:07:22.54,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't the orders not to kill him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.67,0:07:25.67,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,You should've stopped me sooner,\NInsect God.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.08,0:07:30.08,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Too late now, he's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.88,0:07:35.08,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Phew... Come on,\Nlet's all get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.83,0:07:44.21,TopCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,BLEEP BLEEP
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.33,0:07:46.17,TopCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,WHACK\NBLIP BLOP
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.25,0:07:47.96,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why did he want to{\i0}\N{\i1}watch me play a game?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.04,0:07:49.17,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's he up to?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.63,0:07:51.50,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,So I cleared the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.63,0:07:53.58,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,So? You happy now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.88,0:07:55.25,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it over already?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.54,0:07:57.54,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't understand it at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.13,0:08:01.25,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So it's still too soon for me to{\i0}\N{\i1}join the simulated battles{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.38,0:08:04.00,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}that Master Saitama and King{\i0}\N{\i1}usually play.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.29,0:08:05.83,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I need to level up more.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.04,0:08:07.46,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So many things I need to work on.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.75,0:08:10.08,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,It's getting late.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.29,0:08:13.63,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't find Garou\Njust by searching blindly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.71,0:08:16.58,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,He's most likely holed up with\Nthe monsters at their hideout.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.75,0:08:18.75,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Master's resolve seemed unshakable.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.92,0:08:21.71,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Until he discovers and destroys\Nthe Monster Association's base
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.79,0:08:23.13,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,he might not return.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.46,0:08:26.71,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Saitama is strong\Nbut with that personality
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.79,0:08:28.17,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a little worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.25,0:08:30.63,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,If he were to fall into\Nthe monsters' trap by chance...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.75,0:08:35.96,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.29,0:08:37.29,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.42,0:08:38.75,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,He came back\Nlike it was nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.88,0:08:40.79,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you successful?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.08,0:08:42.63,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.92,0:08:43.96,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Phew...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.08,0:08:46.96,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, that was a disaster...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.46,0:08:49.00,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,What a mess I got into.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.08,0:08:50.08,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,- What?!\N- What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.17,0:08:52.79,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you really\Nfound Garou?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.13,0:08:55.83,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You guys are still here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.29,0:08:57.63,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too cramped in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.75,0:09:00.71,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Master! There is blood on you.\NIs it from the Hero Hunter?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.79,0:09:02.67,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I ran into a monster\Non my way home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.75,0:09:04.33,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it from\Nthe Monster Association?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.50,0:09:07.50,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,No, there are always\Nmonsters around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.83,0:09:09.08,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.79,0:09:12.21,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, that's not the problem at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.46,0:09:15.83,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened that\Nwas so disastrous?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.17,0:09:17.88,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,You were all fired up when you left.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.08,0:09:19.63,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Who did what to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.71,0:09:22.88,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,The thing is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.17,0:09:25.96,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I dropped my wallet somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.54,0:09:28.54,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,It had about 6,000 yen inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.17,0:09:33.38,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all? I thought\Nyou had a run in with Garou.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.50,0:09:35.88,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!\NNow that you mention it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.96,0:09:37.13,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.88,0:09:40.17,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That dine-and-dasher!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.29,0:09:41.88,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,You know who it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.33,0:09:44.25,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was chasing him...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.96,0:09:48.54,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,The napa cabbage I bought!\NI left it in a family restaurant!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.79,0:09:50.79,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no. I'll go recover it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.92,0:09:53.46,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Genos.\NYou cannot with those injuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.58,0:09:55.29,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,All this over napa cabbage?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.33,0:09:57.71,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like you're all having fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.13,0:10:02.17,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,You're back again, Hellish Blizzard?\NWhat do you want this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.29,0:10:04.54,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Saitama... How dare you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.67,0:10:09.83,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Is... Is that the napa cabbage?\NWhy does Blizzard have it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.25,0:10:12.00,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, you forgot this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.17,0:10:13.79,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay, you saved the day!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.92,0:10:16.04,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like having hot pot tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.67,0:10:18.92,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,And what's a hot pot\Nwithout napa cabbage!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.00,0:10:21.96,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have\Nanything else to say to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.29,0:10:24.54,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Thanks for the napa cabbage.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.25,0:10:31.42,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Apologize for sticking me\Nwith the bill at the restaurant!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.58,0:10:34.54,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, forgot about that.\NS-Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.71,0:10:36.92,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,You even left in the middle\Nof our conversation again!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.04,0:10:39.33,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Were we talking\Nabout something?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.46,0:10:41.38,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,See, I knew you weren't listening!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.58,0:10:45.88,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, you owe me one.\NDon't you forget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.42,0:10:48.83,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She knows{\i0}\N{\i1}she's not in our league.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.92,0:10:50.13,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why does{\i0}\N{\i1}she keep coming around?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.88,0:10:52.96,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Does she also want to{\i0}\N{\i1}become Master's disciple?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.25,0:10:55.58,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It'd be a hassle{\i0}\N{\i1}if Master's workload increases.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.67,0:10:57.88,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I must prevent that at all costs.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.17,0:11:00.63,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,High-speed approach detected.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.75,0:11:01.71,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Something is coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.79,0:11:02.79,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Damn it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.88,0:11:05.25,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With these injuries,{\i0}\N{\i1}I won't be able to fight properly.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.50,0:11:07.13,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Bang and his brother are injured.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.25,0:11:11.25,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Blizzard likely wouldn't stand a chance{\i0}\N{\i1}if the enemy is Demon level or above.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.75,0:11:15.13,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Master has suffered serious psychological{\i0}\N{\i1}damage from losing his wallet.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.25,0:11:17.46,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The only one{\i0}\N{\i1}who can fight right now is...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.25,0:11:22.08,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,King! An enemy approaches,\Ngo outside and intercept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.21,0:11:23.21,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.33,0:11:25.79,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,- We cannot allow a fight in here.\N- Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.88,0:11:28.63,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,- Just go outside!\N- Wait, there's no need to push.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.71,0:11:30.04,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's calm down.\NWhat's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.17,0:11:31.96,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.\NThere's only one enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.04,0:11:33.04,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,But why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.46,0:11:34.58,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on, Genos?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.71,0:11:37.50,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,A monster has come,\Nbut I asked King to take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.63,0:11:38.71,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.50,0:11:42.25,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,It was right outside the front door.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.63,0:11:43.63,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a visitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.71,0:11:45.71,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...? King!\NWhy would you invite it in?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.79,0:11:49.38,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,No, wait. Looks like you've been\Nbadly damaged again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.46,0:11:51.83,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,You mustn't push yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.21,0:11:54.13,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me, Genos.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.25,0:11:56.50,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Kuseno!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.67,0:11:58.67,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,You know him?\NWhat a relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.79,0:11:59.88,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.00,0:12:01.92,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I was worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.13,0:12:06.42,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Soon after I repaired you,\NI received another distress signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.54,0:12:09.67,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,So I wanted to personally check in\Non you and see what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.79,0:12:11.75,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry to worry you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.96,0:12:14.00,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I said I wouldn't lose again,\Nand yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.08,0:12:15.38,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.50,0:12:19.21,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I had improved your systems\Nand firepower considerably...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.50,0:12:21.13,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.25,0:12:24.08,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Your life is more important\Nthan winning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.38,0:12:27.75,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,So what happened to the enemy\Nthat damaged you so badly?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.21,0:12:30.29,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,As usual, Master Saitama defeated it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.54,0:12:32.42,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... So you must be...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.00,0:12:35.25,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Genos's master, Saitama.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.46,0:12:36.71,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always wanted to\Nmeet you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.83,0:12:38.29,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Mind taking your shoes off?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.42,0:12:40.92,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! So sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.96,0:12:43.96,TopCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,ONE-PUNCH MAN
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.17,0:12:45.38,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Kuseno.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.50,0:12:47.96,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I used to be just a humble\Nmechanical engineer
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.13,0:12:51.08,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,but due to circumstances, I now support\NGenos in his pursuit of justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.17,0:12:52.92,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Saitama.\NNice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.00,0:12:54.04,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.13,0:12:58.04,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,It warms my heart that Genos\Nhas found such a respectable mentor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.42,0:12:59.92,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,When Genos and I first met...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.04,0:13:02.96,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,- He came to pick you up Genos!\N- we had no allies at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.04,0:13:06.42,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,- It's cramped in here, so let's wrap!\N- We wandered through the darkness...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.50,0:13:07.96,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,- Later, Kuseno!\N- We battled evil...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.04,0:13:10.83,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor, please summarize\Nin 20 characters or less.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.04,0:13:12.71,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on.\NDon't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.83,0:13:15.46,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Since I knew that I would be\Nvisiting Saitama's place
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.58,0:13:17.08,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I brought a little something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.21,0:13:19.38,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it some kind of\Nenhancement part for Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.50,0:13:20.92,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I'm human, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.04,0:13:24.67,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,The ultimate premium deluxe beef gift set.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.79,0:13:26.33,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Top quality.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.63,0:13:29.04,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Think of it as a token of gratitude\Nfor taking care of Genos.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.13,0:13:31.13,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you please accept it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.21,0:13:33.38,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Fancy meat, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.50,0:13:36.13,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't had meat in ages...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.33,0:13:37.83,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuseno...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.92,0:13:39.25,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,...I mean, Dr. Kuseno.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.92,0:13:44.13,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,As Genos's mentors,\NI'm sure we have a lot to talk about.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.50,0:13:47.21,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Please feel free to\Ndrop by anytime you like!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.29,0:13:49.17,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What a sucker.{\i0}\N{\i1}That was too easy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.25,0:13:52.92,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now I feel silly for thinking{\i0}\N{\i1}it'd be hard to recruit him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.29,0:13:55.17,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's put this\Nin the hot pot too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.42,0:13:57.13,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go chop the vegetables.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.46,0:14:00.42,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to use\Nthat premium beef for a hot pot?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.50,0:14:02.63,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,What a waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.46,0:14:05.75,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any red wine here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.92,0:14:07.33,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.46,0:14:08.46,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.58,0:14:11.13,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not thinking of staying\Nfor dinner, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.42,0:14:13.88,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,If you have no business here,\Nit's time to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.00,0:14:16.71,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, King, old guys,\Ngo on home!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.42,0:14:19.54,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,We had a little chat with Garou.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.67,0:14:21.75,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,And he failed the test.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.17,0:14:24.83,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Well actually, in the heat of\Nthe moment, we killed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.21,0:14:31.08,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,We said we just wanted to talk,\Nbut then he suddenly attacked us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.17,0:14:33.71,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,How despicable, right, Insect God?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.96,0:14:37.42,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Are those worthless lies\Nall you've got?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.96,0:14:40.75,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me what really happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.92,0:14:44.63,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,He was just some half-assed guy\Ncalling himself a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.75,0:14:48.67,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,He could turn on us at any moment,\Ndepending on the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.29,0:14:50.29,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.42,0:14:54.00,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,You got a problem because\Nwe took care of him on our own?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.17,0:14:57.00,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,No complaints.\NI'm glad you both went.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.13,0:15:00.50,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,You two seem pretty beaten up.\NWas he strong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.54,0:15:04.08,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,That lean body of his packed\Nway more power than I expected
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.17,0:15:05.25,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,and took me off guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.50,0:15:08.21,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I know why\Nyou sent the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.33,0:15:09.96,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,So is he really dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.04,0:15:12.67,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't double-check,\Nbut I'm pretty sure he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.92,0:15:15.50,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because Insect God\Nwas slow to stop me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.58,0:15:18.50,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,You wanted to kill him from the start!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.96,0:15:20.96,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Old dude...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.08,0:15:25.42,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what's with the kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.79,0:15:28.04,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,He saw us, so we brought him in.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.58,0:15:29.71,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you laughing about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.79,0:15:31.29,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Get rid of him immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.42,0:15:33.42,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, don't get so mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.50,0:15:36.21,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I brought him so I can take\Nmy time tormenting him later.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.29,0:15:37.83,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I gotta let off steam
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.92,0:15:41.33,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,or I'll end up impulsively\Nslashing someone here again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.88,0:15:44.04,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no time left\Nfor playing around.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.58,0:15:48.29,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,A Hero Association surveillance robot\Nwas spotted right near our hideout.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.54,0:15:52.13,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll pinpoint this location\Nin less than a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.54,0:15:54.96,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,That means the Class-S heroes\Nwe've all been waiting for
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.04,0:15:56.21,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,will finally be sent our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.29,0:15:58.50,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,And they're formidable opponents.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.96,0:16:01.33,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, prepare for battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.67,0:16:03.58,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it true it was an easy win?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.71,0:16:06.58,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, Gyoro-Gyoro picks opponents\Nbased on compatibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.71,0:16:08.21,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Compatibility, my ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.50,0:16:10.83,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Cowering in front of mere humans!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.13,0:16:16.17,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Strong monsters like me will\Ntake 'em down in a head-on clash.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.33,0:16:17.63,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Pathetic!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.29,0:16:21.21,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,If that story is true, then I should\Nbe able to become one too...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.58,0:16:23.92,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,The Monster King Phoenix Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.25,0:16:25.79,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up, you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.96,0:16:28.46,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I want one kill from each of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.58,0:16:29.96,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Put your life on the line!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.75,0:16:33.46,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,And the credit will be all mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.88,0:16:38.75,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you hear?\NNo killing fellow monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.08,0:16:42.75,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,You pseudo-monsters have\Nno right to defy us real monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.96,0:16:44.46,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Know your place!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.58,0:16:46.54,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Malong Hair, you're so powerful!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.63,0:16:47.96,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you threat level Demon?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.08,0:16:50.08,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Like a tiger with wings\Nand chestnut long hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.29,0:16:53.58,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Straightening my hair gave me power.\NThat is what created Malong Hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.71,0:16:57.21,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, so you monsterized\Nby doing proper hair care?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.67,0:17:02.67,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Nyaan, when Puri-Puri Prisoner\Nshows up let us take care of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.79,0:17:04.04,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.21,0:17:06.25,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,We're strong enough now\Nto get back at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.38,0:17:08.83,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be happy until\NI kill that guy with my own hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.67,0:17:12.04,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.\NDo as you please and go wild.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.79,0:17:16.79,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,The only real top-tier fighter in\Nthe Hero Association is Flashy Flash.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.29,0:17:18.58,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,All the rest are just small fry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.92,0:17:21.92,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,There are people with supernatural powers\Nand robots on their side.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.71,0:17:24.58,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Robots are irrelevant.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.92,0:17:29.46,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,No machine could ever keep up\Nwith a ninja's speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.50,0:18:31.88,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,What about the\Nsupernatural powers?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.33,0:18:37.71,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll kill them so quickly that they\Nwon't be able to activate their powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.96,0:18:49.67,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,You're G5, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.92,0:18:53.75,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?\NDid you steal that from somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.88,0:18:57.54,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a little something I picked up\Nfor my own interests.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.08,0:19:00.79,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I plan to take it apart\Nand analyze it in detail.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.96,0:19:03.29,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Metal Knight is in pieces?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.83,0:19:05.83,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a valuable sample.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.29,0:19:07.33,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,If you'll excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.58,0:19:15.83,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Waganma, I brought you a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.42,0:19:20.25,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you? I'm Tareo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.42,0:19:22.13,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you captured by the monsters, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.71,0:19:24.96,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...Waganma?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.38,0:19:28.54,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Hey, is it nighttime already?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.88,0:19:30.17,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.71,0:19:33.04,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,You got any food?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.17,0:19:37.29,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I have candy. I only have one piece,\Nbut if you want it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.63,0:19:41.63,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.71,0:19:43.88,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.50,0:19:46.58,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, you're useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.58,0:19:50.71,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,So...what's gonna happen to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.96,0:19:53.38,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Those monsters sure are dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.46,0:19:54.46,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.54,0:19:56.63,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, of all people,\Nthey kidnapped me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.92,0:19:59.63,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,My dad's a big shot\Nin the Hero Association.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.92,0:20:00.92,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.00,0:20:03.29,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm sure the Hero Association\Nwon't sit back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.42,0:20:05.13,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll come and save me right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.50,0:20:08.42,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'll have them rescue you too,\Nwhile they're at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.50,0:20:11.00,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,- Really?\N- I'll ask the heroes for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.13,0:20:12.50,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.67,0:20:16.54,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,- Then from now on, you work for me.\N- Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.96,0:20:18.04,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,You gotta problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.21,0:20:19.46,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,You wanna be rescued, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.58,0:20:20.63,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.83,0:20:22.50,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.58,0:20:24.50,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you two talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.63,0:20:26.29,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Yikes! A monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.63,0:20:29.67,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but you two\Nare never going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.75,0:20:31.50,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,What a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.58,0:20:34.00,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't let me\Ngo home right now
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.13,0:20:35.42,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,the heroes are gonna come!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.96,0:20:39.54,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,You're all gonna die.\NThe heroes and your dad too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.67,0:20:43.54,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,All because they came to save you.\NEveryone will die!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.79,0:20:48.54,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Class-S heroes are coming, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.67,0:20:51.58,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are going to\Nget your butts kicked!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.71,0:20:55.29,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, Metal Bat alone\Ncould take all of you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.42,0:20:58.08,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I know. I saw him up close.\NIt'll be a piece of cake for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.21,0:21:01.38,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, sure thing.\NOhh, I'm so scared of Metal Bat.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.29,0:21:07.71,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...Waganma...\NI saw on the news...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.88,0:21:10.96,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,All of 'em... Lightning Genji,\NHeavy Kong, Metal Bat...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.54,0:21:13.71,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,And also Metal Knight...\Njust a while ago were...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.08,0:21:17.58,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,So? The Hero Association has\NTornado and Blast too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.79,0:21:20.04,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, and there's King too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.50,0:21:21.58,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.67,0:21:23.46,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet just hearing\Nthat name scares you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.71,0:21:28.29,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, kid. Do you even know why\Nthe Monster Association was created?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.50,0:21:32.04,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,To wipe every last one\Nof those pests off the map.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.33,0:21:36.58,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,We knew from the start that\Nthe Class-S heroes are insanely strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.71,0:21:38.38,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm still telling you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.50,0:21:40.54,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Every last hero will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.08,0:21:42.88,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got crazy monsters\Nfar more dangerous
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.96,0:21:44.67,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,than the Class-S heroes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.92,0:21:49.63,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially our top monsters,\Nwho are threat level Dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.88,0:21:59.71,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Possessing miraculous strength....
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.83,0:22:04.00,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,They're like God's own works of art!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.21,0:22:06.83,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Humans don't stand\Na chance against them.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.96,0:22:09.58,BottomCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,Even King will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.00,0:24:00.83,TopCenter,,0000,0000,0000,,COUNTERATTACK SIGNAL

